{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_05_03",
  "title": "伊吹渚 3話 まな板に残る桃の皮",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "渚！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "一体どうしたんだ！？\n顔色が凄く悪いじゃないか……あ、すぐ病院に！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What on earth happened!?\nYour complexion looks really bad… Ah‚ let's go to the hospital right away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、体は全然なんともありません……\n心はぽきぽきに折れちゃいましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ my body is perfectly fine…\nBut my heart feels completely broken…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "何があったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "その……あれです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… it's that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　まな板の上に、あれは……桃の皮？\nあ、もしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? On the cutting board… is that… peach peel?\nAh‚ could it be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、食べちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I ate it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "最近、私眠りが浅くて……\n寝ぼけることが多くなったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ my sleep has been shallow…\nI've been sleepwalking more often.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 41.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 41.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "私、心配で夜も眠れません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't sleep at night because I'm so worried!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 46.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "桃を剥いて食べてました。七個も……\nそれで、今朝目が覚めたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was peeling and eating peaches. Seven of them…\nAnd then‚ when I woke up this morning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "な、七個も！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Seven of them!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ、三日前、食レポの仕事があって\nその刺激が強過ぎたんです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ three days ago‚ I had a food review job‚\nand the stimulation was too strong…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんが、大好物のおしるこを美味しそうに\n食べてる横で、私は一口で我慢して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While Sumire-chan was happily eating her favorite rice porridge next to me…\nI restrained myself with just one bite…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8343333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "その時のすみれちゃんの幸せそうな笑顔が\n焼きついて、羨まし過ぎて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Sumire-chan's blissful smile at that moment…\nIt stuck in my mind‚ and I felt so envious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "私も大好きな桃のことばかり考えるようになって\n夢にまで見たんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I started thinking only about the peaches that I love so much…\nIt even appeared in my dreams…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "昨日の夢では、莉央さんが桃とパンケーキを食べながら\nキレッキレに踊ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In yesterday's dream‚ Rio-san was dancing flawlessly\nwhile eating peaches and pancakes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5393333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "とんでもない夢だな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a ridiculous dream…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、あんなに{user}さんに\n協力してもらったのに、私、私……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ even though I received\nso much help from {user}-san‚ I… I…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4343333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "取り返しのつかないことをしてしまいました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've done something irreparable!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "どれどれ……うん、この桃美味いな\n渚が食べたくなるの、よく分かるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me see… Mmm‚ these peaches are delicious.\nI understand why you would crave them‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "え？　{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺も今、食べた。これでおあいこだ\n渚、真面目なのはいいけど、自分を追い詰めないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I ate some too just now. So we're even.\nNagisa‚ it's good to be serious‚ but don't push yourself into a corner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも！\n私、ダイエットに失敗しちゃったんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But!\nI failed my diet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7343333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、衣装を着るまで分からないだろ\n昨日、ちょうど衣装が届いたんだ。試着してみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You won't know that until you try on the outfit.\nJust yesterday‚ the outfits arrived. How about trying them on first?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "私だけ先に……いいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I try it on first…? Is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、みんなには内緒にしておいてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ please keep it a secret from everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペスト、夏フェス当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Moon Tempest‚ Summer Festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 143.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 143.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 143.3666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\nこっち！　こっちですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nOver here! This way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ本番だな。調子はどうだ？",
